
    Three rapists were each sentenced to life imprisonment in
the Makerong Regional court .The heavy sentence emanate from an incident which occurred
in October last year in Ga-Magongoa Zone 2,  outside Mokopane.According to the police spokesperson Brigadier Motlafela
Mojapelo,  Frans Makhafola(33), Alfred
Lesiba Magogoa(27) and Ephraim Malotsa(27) grabbed a 35-year-old woman who was
on her way home from a funeral, dragged her into the nearby bushes where they
